gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Lakers 134, Trail Blazers 110
gameRecap.excerpt: The Lakers defeated the Trail Blazers, 134-110. D’Angelo Russell led the way with 34 points (6-11 3PM) and eight assists for the Lakers, with LeBron James adding 28 points, five rebounds, and five assists in the victory. Malcolm Brogdon tallied 23 points, nine assists, and seven rebounds for the Trail Blazers in the losing effort. The Lakers improve to 22-22, while the Trail Blazers fall to 12-30.
